{"tid":929073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該同佢講我鍾意佢？","createTime":"2018-12-05T10:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T13:55:02.000Z","uid":217593,"like":8,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf9b65496b7d2b422efbb624676904694901209","tid":929073,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:15:27.000Z","msg":"鍾意緊個女仔，我大佢一年。原本對佢幾有好感，跟住個幾月前喺IG Direct佢，佢成日秒回我，當我悶嘅時候佢又會同我不停傾計。<br />\n<br />\n我日日都噓寒問暖，重諗住遲啲約佢出街。但頭先傾傾下，佢話佢鍾意咗個人，重問我係邊個，以為自己有機啦終於！點知佢話佢鍾意咗個TB。個下真係呆撚咗，明明之佢之前都係鍾意男仔，乜性向哩啲話轉就轉㗎咩！？我問佢係唔係肯定鍾意個TB，佢話係！！！我真係O撚曬嘴！<br />\n<br />\n佢講完之後有諗過同唔同佢表白好，怕講咗會尷尬無Friend做，但唔講又驚佢咁就被人搶走。而家心情好複雜，唔知點覆佢好。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打，我應唔應該同佢講我鍾意佢？<br />\n同埋我可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac8bf743ec78aaf56c082af1485e8e3c8eb83aa","tid":929073,"uid":35105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"渣佢個波"},{"pid":"2146cc9b7098bd7ca1989197e554ff1390fe9524","tid":929073,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:21:54.000Z","msg":"緊係講，還掂唔講之後都冇friend做架啦"},{"pid":"a218d6575f54526cf92e2600cc01b783b2e53229","tid":929073,"uid":85232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"屌，仔都話啫，你唔係輸俾個TB嘛？"},{"pid":"b4871f169544bbc0693d5ba2babe60d3d092c7af","tid":929073,"uid":217593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bac8bf743ec78aaf56c082af1485e8e3c8eb83aa","tid":929073,"uid":35105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:16:53.000Z","msg":"渣佢個波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a54a6a2c8856ea19df1cd48104b499c848d0a14","tid":929073,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime